name: Psychic Parasite
summary: Atthe peak ofhis life, aman istransported tothe future. Aworld that had faced anapocalypse, barely clinging totheir humanity iswhat greetedhim. The post-apocalyptic world, the Earth ofthe future was shrouded inmystery. Inorder toreturn tohis timeline, anera where hehad left his footsteps behind, hehad tounravel the secrets ofthe world. The only problem being, this was anera dominated bythe Parasites.
